Opinion: The coronavirus and trade war punish China, damaging its status as a source of growth 
  Comments 
Published: March 8, 2020 at 6:58 p.m. ET 
By 
Cody Willard 
Will developed countries shun China? If so, the U.S. may benefit as a result 
Xi Jinping, China's president, in better days. 
Bloomberg 
 
